        <h2>Welcome to Nepal Hike Hub</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Nepal Hike Hub, your trusted companion for exploring the breathtaking landscapes of Nepal. We are passionate about connecting adventure seekers with the natural beauty, rich culture, and unforgettable trekking experiences that Nepal has to offer.</p>
        
        <p>At Nepal Hike Hub, we specialize in providing reliable information, curated hiking routes, and personalized trekking guidance for beginners and experienced hikers alike. From the iconic Himalayan trails to hidden local paths, our goal is to make every journey safe, enjoyable, and meaningful.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to promote sustainable and responsible tourism while helping travelers discover the true essence of Nepal. We aim to support local communities, preserve natural environments, and create authentic experiences that go beyond just hiking.</p>
        
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Detailed guides on popular and off-the-beaten-path hiking trails</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Easy-to-use booking and planning support</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Tips on safety, gear, and preparation</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Cultural insights to enrich your journey</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Local recommendations for food, stays, and experiences</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
        <p>We combine local knowledge with a passion for adventure. Whether you are planning your first hike or looking for a new challenge, Nepal Hike Hub provides the tools and support you need to explore with confidence.</p>
        
        <p>Join us and start your journey into the heart of Nepal—where every trail tells a story.</p>
        
        <h3>Nepal Hike Hub – Explore More, Experience More.</h3>
